race.comment: Tough start to proceedings but no shortage of well-related types with a sister to Verry Elleegant and a half-sister to Another Wil engaged. They'll probably both be better for the experience here, though, and siding with HARMONY (6), who finished fourth last start over 1600m at Ballarat, an improvement on her fifth on debut at Warrnambool the run before. PRONOUNCED (4) debuted 3.5 weeks ago when he finished seventh over 1427m at Sale. Will be much better for that run. FLIGHT SERGEANT (3) was unsighted on debut but was put away after that and looks to have come back a better product if jumpouts are any indication, including a couple of Flemington second placings. CATATOMIC (2) was responsible for a better run last start at the second run of the prep, beaten 4.5 lengths into fifth over 1300m at Warrnambool. In the mix.
